  "title": "URGENT Operation Admin Executive",
  "description": "<ul><li>Manage daily administrative and operational tasks.</li><li>Plan and schedule workers, vehicles, and drivers based on site needs.</li><li>Coordinate truck and driver deployment with other departments.</li><li>Maintain vehicle records — inspection, insurance, road tax, parking fines, and logbooks.</li><li>Handle document preparation, filing, and record updates.</li><li>Assist with BCA approvals, site permits, and office maintenance matters.</li><li>Work closely with dormitory and liaise with workers on any issues.</li><li>Provide general administrative support as required.</li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>1-2 years of relevant working experience.</li><li>Excellent communication and customer service skills.</li><li>Strong organizational & administrative skills.</li><li>Proficiency in Microsoft Office & Management Software.</li><li>Ability to multitask is a must.</li><li>Good to have class 3/3C license.</li></ul>",
